  <title translate="true">Uses of Auxiliary Parameters</title>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:12px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Auxiliary parameters are used with MODPATH and the Groundwater Transport process. &#160;In MODPATH, the variable IFACE is specified with an auxiliary parameter. &#160;In the Groundwater Transport process, concentration is specified with an auxiliary parameter. &#160;The option </text><text styleclass="Keywords" translate="true">COMPACT BUDGET AUXILIARY</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> must be used in the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="OC" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Output Control</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> when IFACE is used for MODPATH.</text></para>
  </body>
